---
// FeaturedVideo.astro
---
<section class="py-24 bg-white/5 border-t border-white/10 relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-end gap-6 mb-12">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-amber-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm mb-3">Latest Video</h3>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white tracking-tight">Watch &amp; <span class="text-amber-500">Learn</span></h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/videos" class="text-amber-500 font-semibold hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 group whitespace-nowrap">
        View all videos <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <a href="/videos/stab-framework-google-ads-optimization" class="group block rounded-2xl bg-[#020617] border border-white/10 hover:border-amber-500/40 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-amber-500/10 transition-all overflow-hidden duration-300">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-5 h-full">
        <!-- Thumbnail -->
        <div class="md:col-span-3 relative aspect-video md:aspect-auto">
          <img 
            src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/AYS75avOWdQ/maxresdefault.jpg" 
            alt="The S T A B Framework for Google Ads Optimization" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-amber-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-black/70 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 flex items-center gap-1.5 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-red-500"><path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94-2C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94 2C1 8.13 1 12 1 12s0 3.87.46 5.58a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94 2C5.12 20 12 20 12 20s6.88 0 8.6-.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94-2C23 15.87 23 12 23 12s0-3.87-.46-5.58zM9.54 15.5vp-7l6.58 3.5-6.58 3.5z"/></svg>
            <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">YouTube</span>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-black/70 rounded px-2 py-1 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">37:34</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="md:col-span-2 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-500 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
              Google Ads
            </span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4 leading-tight group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">
            The S T A B Framework for Google Ads Optimization
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Are you paying Google just to lose money? The secret to scaling isn't in the AI &mdash; it's in the STAB Framework: Spend, Targeting, Auto/Ads, and Bidding. Learn the exact sequence to stop the bleeding and manufacture profit.
          </p>
          <div class="text-amber-500 font-semibold group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform flex items-center gap-1">
            Watch Now &rarr;
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
